com.software.reuze

Class dg_EntityDomainRectangular

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.dg_EntityDomainRectangular

  • public class dg_EntityDomainRectangular
extends Object
    Objects of this class represent a rectangular region of the world. It can also used to store the view-port or display area of the screen.
    Although the attributes are public this is for speed of reading and they should only be changed using the methods provided in this class.
    Author:
    Peter Lager
